<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Chains of Technology</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jan 13, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Rousseau’s  <i>Social Contract</i> opens with “Man is born to be free, and everywhere he is in chains.” It’s amazing that he could recognize that without ever seeing a group of people with their smartphones.
